[normal]Online Safety Bill[bold]1
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]I support the current Online Safety Bill 2012 promoted by Baroness Howe of Idlicote
[normal], or a similar provision to protect children from harm and inappropriate ‘so called’ adult 
[normal]material.  We need to help parents who can’t or won’t help themselves by providing the needed responsible legislation.
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]Drains and Sewers[bold]In the same way that the 
[normal]Government provides drains and sewers for the physical health of the nation, they must provide for the moral health
[normal] of our nation
[normal] by containing filth and impurities.
